Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:06.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親  您叫我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.54,0:00:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  把那個打開看看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.34,0:00:20.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.47,0:00:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我夫人穿過的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.63,0:00:24.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿穿看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.80,0:00:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:27.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.25,0:00:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在尺寸應該很合身了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.51,0:00:30.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.61,0:00:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.29,0:00:38.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  沒什麼變化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.38,0:00:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作順利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.22,0:00:43.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作啊  還沒有上軌道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.90,0:00:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和對策室的紀之關係好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.00,0:00:50.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉  我有話跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.73,0:00:54.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於和飯綱家結親的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.50,0:00:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你們雙方都沒有感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.71,0:01:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不考慮當事人的心意繼續此事似乎不太妥當
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.41,0:01:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想再聽聽你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.72,0:01:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親  您收養了舉目無親的我並把我撫養長大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.18,0:01:26.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我瞭解此次結親的目的重在加深親戚間牽絆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.95,0:01:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無反對的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我欣然接受此次婚約
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a10\fad(1000,0)}\N\N\N\N\N\N「執　念」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.06,0:03:12.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快變強吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  在想什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.34,0:03:26.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紀  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.57,0:03:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管狐又多了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.47,0:03:34.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是最近出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:37.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該讓它熟悉工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.45,0:03:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顧靈獸還真麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.06,0:03:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的靈獸只負責報告情報
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說麻煩  神樂你更甚幾倍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.65,0:03:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  還遠著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:56.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別考慮得太複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:02.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.15,0:04:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹…什麼  怎麼了黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:14.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…也沒…有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.89,0:04:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  永遠是長不大的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:30.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納布向你問好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納布也向你問好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.42,0:04:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:38.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是新的靈力分佈圖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.70,0:04:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  昨天確實記得這片地方有些異樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龜戶的靜止鋒的話在今天早上消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰把靈除掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.54,0:04:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除我們之外還有很多自由退魔師存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,市谷的同行者也壯大了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.74,0:05:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡靈行動起來也束手束腳了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.33,0:05:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.64,0:05:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂  你現代語考試得了幾分？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.36,0:05:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.15,0:05:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂的事我可是瞭如指掌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:13.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看試卷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.74,0:05:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都知道的話不看也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪理連篇的  是這張嘴說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛…好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.47,0:05:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.32,0:05:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:26.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉你涂什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒涂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:33.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納布聞到香味了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納布也聞到香味了噗露露
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:39.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是騙不了納布先生的鼻子的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…剛剛買的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做…做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.59,0:05:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睫毛…比平時長了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.50,0:05:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係嘛  我也會化妝的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.77,0:05:58.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  今天要和小紀約會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:06:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  沒這種安排
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.10,0:06:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小紀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  感覺什麼好難聞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼  化妝品的怪味
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.75,0:06:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…是我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:19.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是神樂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:22.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是工作的地方  別把這種東西帶過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的血統在鼻子方面可是很敏感的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂  你不知道怎麼涂香水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.79,0:06:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用得過量就像小孩子胡鬧似的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.19,0:06:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會適得其反囉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:38.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧香淡留就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用太多的話就跟濃妝大媽的味道一樣了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好燙好燙好燙…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  不小心撒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少騙人了  你跟我有仇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.32,0:06:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:02.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事就會向人潑咖啡的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  這是你身上的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:13.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己在那邊散佈氣味  就別推在神樂身上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:14.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你化濃妝沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦喲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.86,0:07:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火大了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.24,0:07:28.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火大了又如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.73,0:07:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  別在事務所裡把靈獸召出來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人都把小亂和小不點收起來收起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:56.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神宮寺室長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.35,0:08:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你們兩個到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:08.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡而言之就是性格不合啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.63,0:08:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場婚事可以繼續談下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:20.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀定大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:22.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無異議
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:26.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能入贅到統領一族的諫山家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.05,0:08:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實乃求之不得的好事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想儘快完成儀式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.97,0:08:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼急
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:39.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等黃泉從學校畢業再舉行婚禮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底是家世和權勢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想能衷心為他們祝福啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.74,0:08:51.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄長大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.90,0:08:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了啊  幽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.00,0:08:58.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  兄長大人也依然健朗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.99,0:09:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說與飯綱家的那樁親事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.82,0:09:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說要招婿入贅而讓黃泉繼承家主之位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.10,0:09:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.34,0:09:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:14.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉的確還很年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:18.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻擁有一副不辱諫山家之名的好身手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不用擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:22.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是黃泉可是養女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.53,0:09:26.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今還翻這陳年老賬做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.03,0:09:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是不想讓她繼承家業
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.53,0:09:32.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當初也不會把獅子王託付給她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.16,0:09:37.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算這樣兄長大人難道要把家主之位傳給沒有諫山血統的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.82,0:09:47.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽  難道說拋棄了諫山家使命拒絕戰鬥的你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今卻想繼承家主之位了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕非如此  兄長大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.82,0:09:55.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想不通為什麼偏偏把家業傳給一個沒血統的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.68,0:09:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:10:00.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這個拋棄使命的人的確為諫山家蒙羞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.48,0:10:03.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我也有個女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女兒冥也擁有不辱諫山家之名的身手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.18,0:10:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您務必三思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:14.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您說錯了  父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.93,0:10:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉小姐即使在退魔師中也算得上數一數二的劍術高手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還負責照顧著喪母的土宮家小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:29.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在親戚中也是備受信賴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豈是我這等人能相提並論的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:38.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧  奈落叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:44.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未婚夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.81,0:10:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  未婚夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:47.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婚約者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母定下的結婚對象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夠浪漫的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像是少女漫畫情節
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.83,0:10:57.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人郎才女貌  就像是流行電視劇一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:10:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是月九嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:10:58.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（月九：每週一晚上九點播放的電視連續劇，是黃金檔）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最近發展得不太順利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正煩惱要怎麼樣才能讓他們好好相處呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…這樣如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.39,0:11:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣  現在開始說明作戰方針
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家無異議吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先由變裝成無賴的小一去襲擊黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.29,0:11:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛好路過的小紀解決了小一救出黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.21,0:11:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉立刻傾心於充滿男子漢氣概的小紀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人以Happy  End結束
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:38.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我攻擊…諫山？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:41.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.95,0:11:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不不…會喪命的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那改變計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納布先生代替小一去襲擊黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.03,0:11:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:57.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把錢交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:11:59.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納布No  No
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.73,0:12:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納布也No  No
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.44,0:12:04.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那麼岩端先生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.13,0:12:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧  男女的事外人還是不要插手為好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且萬一他們分手了…飯綱說不定會喜歡上我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:19.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你原來在打這個算盤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.98,0:12:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  在商量什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.02,0:12:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  兄長到底中什麼邪了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.24,0:12:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用如此生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們退魔師本來生命就不會長久
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.35,0:12:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我繼承了家主之位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.66,0:12:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一在執行任務中不幸喪生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.31,0:12:49.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家主最後還是會落在黃泉小姐手上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.93,0:12:51.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在胡說什麼  冥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反過來考慮  萬一黃泉小姐去世
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:12:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我或許就能繼承了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  只是時間的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.51,0:13:18.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人再這麼冷戰下去  或許會影響到任務的執行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:22.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒辦法  一次解決兩個人是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.56,0:13:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先讓黃泉對小紀回心轉意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然有囉  我的殺手鐧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:43.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納布就位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,納布也就位了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.76,0:13:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認第一目標
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:04.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小桐  準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.48,0:14:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二階堂桐  行動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.50,0:14:14.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是二階堂女士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:16.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你…你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.56,0:14:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯…飯綱君…今天負責巡邏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拘謹  太拘謹啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二階堂小姐  再自然點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是少見啊  二階堂女士居然會穿裙子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.57,0:14:31.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍稍有些私事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也穿這身到對策室來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會使工作場所增色不少哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有效果了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:44.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小紀還真是個花花公子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.35,0:14:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之第一階段進行得還算順利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就是讓諫山看到這一幕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.47,0:14:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉一定會魂不守舍的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體注意  第二目標接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:08.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近猛增起來真是麻煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:10.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與第二目標接觸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.72,0:15:15.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而毫無反應
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小桐  Phase1
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:21.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Phase1  瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.51,0:15:30.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認命中目標
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.46,0:15:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然毫無變化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你演得不夠大膽  再攻擊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.31,0:15:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊進入  Phase2
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:47.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二目標  一如既往地沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:50.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  心裡肯定動搖了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.82,0:15:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊進入Phase3
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:56.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…二階堂女士？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:16:01.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀之  我們就別玩地下情了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.36,0:16:03.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？不…你在說什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.01,0:16:05.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二目標離開戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊無效
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:09.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複一遍  攻擊無效
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.53,0:16:27.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個  剛剛的到底是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…那個原因有很多…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:32.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊很有效
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:34.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標發生變化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.67,0:16:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這不是適得其反嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.33,0:16:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:40.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉怎麼看都更加生氣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:45.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能解釋下這是怎麼一回事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.97,0:16:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼個頭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有未婚妻了還在勾三搭四
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.24,0:16:51.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  吃醋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.16,0:16:54.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃醋？那是什麼？你誤會什麼了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誤會？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.13,0:16:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你毫無感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.59,0:17:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是遵從父親定下的婚約而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.19,0:17:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別給我自信過頭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.77,0:17:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能違背老爹只能乖乖聽話而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對女人動手簡直是人渣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出手這麼重  沒這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  說不定我們一直都會是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.35,0:17:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…性情不怎麼相投
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.12,0:17:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉  小紀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.14,0:17:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一起之後也會時常大打出手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.29,0:17:59.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵架是不會間斷的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.37,0:18:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能忍受這種生活？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.63,0:18:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還能回頭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.93,0:18:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拒絕就趁現在了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.16,0:18:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  的確如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀之  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:24.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.33,0:18:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  全是我不好  都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.28,0:18:31.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以拜託你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.91,0:18:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.25,0:18:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉就像是我的姐姐一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結婚之後小紀就會變成親哥哥一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人增加了  和和氣氣的不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.36,0:18:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才…對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.92,0:19:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  神樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.32,0:19:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我們會和好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:07.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.77,0:19:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.43,0:19:10.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樂  我不會惹你哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千真萬確嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:17.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.47,0:19:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證據呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.59,0:19:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證據？要怎麼做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.37,0:19:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就親一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.63,0:19:29.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想看到你們的和好之吻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.61,0:19:31.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你在胡說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.24,0:19:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:32.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒問題哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣做神樂會滿意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.39,0:19:36.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  紀之
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.44,0:19:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,興奮  興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.59,0:19:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀…紀之
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:52.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.64,0:19:56.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上就是此次作戰成果
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:20:00.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他們又重新開始吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:02.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.87,0:20:42.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是夠嗆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.88,0:20:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是神樂式的擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.54,0:20:46.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.45,0:20:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一身很美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.44,0:20:50.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新對我有興趣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.67,0:20:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真難得啊  竟然把它派到我家來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:20:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:21:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們是自由行動的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人  從來沒到過我這哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.18,0:21:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是它藏得好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.29,0:21:09.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒道理察覺不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是說不過你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了防止看到我的秘密而使幻想破滅？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.91,0:21:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  我想通過自己的雙眼來觀察你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.28,0:21:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們能一直這麼吵下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.24,0:21:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會的  一直…持續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.84,0:21:59.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是時間的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.44,0:22:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那對誰來說都是同等的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.40,0:22:26.51,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか誓ったのよ　自分の心へと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.00,0:22:37.19,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}嘆きの渦にのまれた　君を助けたいと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.36,0:22:47.91,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}重ねる時は変えてゆく　理の歯車が銹びたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.00,0:22:52.90,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}もう戻れない　I hate this world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.13,0:23:00.50,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}全て壊したい　どこにもまだ行けない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.66,0:23:03.90,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}思い出の為に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.95,0:23:11.17,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}幸せだったと　あの頃だけ抱きしめ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.29,0:23:26.66,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,2000)}遠ざかる夢の足音　胸に刻み込んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.40,0:22:26.51,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}曾經對自己的心靈　許下了誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.00,0:22:37.19,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}想要救贖　捲入嘆息漩渦中的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.36,0:22:47.91,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}交錯的時光轉瞬即逝　道理的齒輪鏽跡斑斕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.00,0:22:52.90,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}已經無法後退　我憎恨此世
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.13,0:23:00.50,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,800)}想要摧毀一切　亦無容身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.66,0:23:03.90,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}為了思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.95,0:23:11.17,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}將那時僅有的幸福　深情擁抱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.29,0:23:26.66,OP中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,2000)}將遠去的夢的足音　刻骨銘心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話  喰靈  -零-
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.23,0:23:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「美麗的敵人」


